flowchart TB
    Members([Member Firms])
    Gateway[Order Gateway<br/>auth + risk + validate]
    Sequencer[Sequencer<br/>single-threaded<br/>global ordering]
    InputLog[(Input Log<br/>append-only<br/>durable)]
    MatchEngines[Matching Engines<br/>one thread per symbol<br/>in-memory order books]
    Standby[Hot Standby<br/>lockstep replay]
    MarketData[Market Data Publisher<br/>multicast feed]
    Subscribers([Subscribers])

    Members -->|orders| Gateway
    Gateway --> Sequencer
    Sequencer -->|persist before process| InputLog
    Sequencer --> MatchEngines
    InputLog -.->|replay| Standby
    MatchEngines --> MarketData
    MarketData -.->|multicast| Subscribers

    classDef external fill:#1e2533,stroke:#3a4a6e,color:#cfd6e6
    classDef service fill:#1a3a2e,stroke:#3a6e54,color:#cfe6d6
    classDef store fill:#1e2a3e,stroke:#3a5a8e,color:#cfdcef
    classDef config fill:#3a2e1a,stroke:#6e5a3a,color:#efdfcf

    class Members,Subscribers external
    class Gateway,Sequencer,MatchEngines,Standby,MarketData service
    class InputLog store
